commit_message:
Install and run Sahara from different packages

Now Sahara is splitted to different packages:
* python-sahara - python code;
* sahara-common - common actions (creating user, directoties);
* sahara-api - sahara-api daemon init/start-up logic;
* sahara-engine - sahara-engine daemon init/start-up logic;

implements blueprint separate-sahara-package

Change-Id: I4a01159ff7b377cd7e517d338a6e564a65fc950a

